tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
It's rare to find such friendly doctor like Dr. Dharna. I met her during the last month of my pregnancy as my regular doctor went on to leave and she referred me to her. I was so tensed and worried before meeting her as all of sudden I had to change my doctor along with planning my c-sec delivery due to some medical conditions. With so many doubts in my mind I went to Dr. Dharna's clinic 1 day before my c-sec was planned and it just took her 5 minutes to turn all my doubts into hope, a hope that I can still try for NVD even with some health issues (my LFT was way to high and I had Gestational diabetes too). 

I have never seen a doctor as cool, calm and composed like Dr. Dharna (Thanks Dr. Shikha for leaving my in good hands during the most difficult time). 

More than a doctor you treated my like a friend and like an elder person in family. You encouraged me a lot and that's injected life in me. All my worried went off and I was successfully able to deliver my baby boy with your help.

I would recommend a doctor like you to every women who wants to conceive and deliver a child with so much care, support, guidance and encouragement. Thanks a lot Dharna Mam.
reply_text: Thanks for such kind words Pooja🙏🏻

tags: Doctor friendliness,
context: Pre and Post Delivery Care,Post Pregnancy Classes,
review: I have visited Dr Dharna a lot many times since i was 2 months pregnant till date when i am full time pregnant. I feel very comfortable talking to her . Her friendly behaviour force me  to share every little problem of mine with her and the best part is she sorted the problem and i have  never faced the same issue again.Even the assistants are very good , they have always kept us informed in advance whenever  she is not available / out of station.She has always been so polite and soft in her explanations  with  my husband and mother in law that they too are very much satisfied with her. I would highly recommend this doctor as she really deserves all this appreciation. Keep up the good work maam 👍

tags: Treatment satisfaction,
review: I have been having excessive bleeding from last 6 months. Doctor advised me to go for ultrasound n found that fibroids were causing trouble. She advised me to go with mirena but it didn’t suit me I have waited for 3 months n consulted doctor as bleeding stopped but I had regular pain. Finally that day came I couldn’t stop bleeding even after double dose. Doctor asked me to get done ultrasound n found that fibroids are still causing bleeding  than she asked me to do some test n admit to hospital. There doctor operated me n took out the uterus. She took necessary actions n surgery was successful.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Dr. Dharna Gupta is * **** **** ******* caring and did a great job in the case of my wife's pre conception treatment and complicated pregnancy issues ongoing from a long time. She handled my wife's case very diligently and explained everything to us timely and very clearly. She not only taken great care of health but also is lovely to speak and always been supportive at every appointment or even on a call. Her staff support was great and helpful throughout. we were so happy with her treatment procedure that I have also recommended her to my sister during her pregnancy which is again a complicated pregnancy. Thanks to Dr Dharna and her team for all the support.

tags: Doctor friendliness,
review: Dr. Dharna is wonderful. I am the mother of two children. She was in charge of both of my deliveries. Both of these deliveries are normal. She has been really concerned about my health. I suffered awful nausea and vomiting during my second pregnancy. I was able to get through my morning sickness and deliver a healthy baby thanks to her medication and advice. She's a delight to converse with. It's uncommon to find a doctor that combines medical skill with such individualized patient attention. I strongly advise you to see her as your gynecologist!
reply_text:
Thank you for the feedback. Happy to help😊
Humbled by your kind words dear.🙏🏻

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I had been referring another doctor for my delivery. Somehow I was left in doubt and had many unanswered questions. I was suggested Dr. Dharna's name and I went there for a second opinion. The way she clarified all my doubts and put me to rest. Somehow I knew she would be the one who would operate me. She did not send me for scores of unnecessary tests, neither did she scare me mentioning complexities etc. Like my last obygn was doing. She took me in confidence and my c-section went so smooth. I did not have any complications, her instructions were very clear and easy. She is my obygn from now on.
reply_text: Thanks for your kind words Nivedita. 🙏🏻

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: We are very much satisfied and happy with Dr. Dharna Gupta. When I came to know my wife is pregnant last year in june we decided to get treatment/regular check up by Dr. Dharna. From day one we noticed that she is very experienced, expert, friendly, positive and encouraging. Due to last two failed attempts to become parents we were not sure if we are ready for the 3rd time but Dr. Dharna encouraged us and made us think positive. I still remember her words on our first appointment "This baby has to come". I got my wife checked up regularly by Dr. Dharna for 8-9 months and yes finally baby has come this February. Thanks again Dr. Dharna and keep smiling :)

tags: Value for money,Wait time,
review: The waiting time is high . we already waited for the doctor for a routine checkup and after the checkup we asked for a bill then attendant said wait for some time for the bill and after 30 min I received a ping from her attendant and she said please come on Monday to collect the bill .This is too much disappointing for me .
reply_text:
Dear Patient Soni,
You’ve been visiting us for your pregnancy since January. And the waiting time has never been more than 10 minutes ever. Mostly you were the first patient of the day. Sometimes if the doctor is attending to another patient, a little wait may happen . I hope you understand that. Also we give soft copy of invoices (an effort to be planet friendly). Hard copies are given on request. That also you’ve received always.

Patients may have to wait a little but they always receive the right treatment.
All the best to you🙏🏻
